00:31:27,740 --> 00:31:29,960
 12 kaže ovako

662
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,180
 nego se uvijek obrati

663
00:31:31,180 --> 00:31:32,020
 na pobožnika

664
00:31:32,020 --> 00:31:33,060
 o kome znadeš

665
00:31:33,060 --> 00:31:33,980
 da vrši zapovjed

666
00:31:33,980 --> 00:31:35,160
 koji je s tobom jedne duše

667
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,040
 i koji će na tobom

668
00:31:36,040 --> 00:31:37,340
 plakat kad posrneš.

669
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:39,220
 On u puću je ovdje

670
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,080
 na pobožnika

671
00:31:40,080 --> 00:31:41,200
 kad donosiš odluku,

672
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:42,680
 da ne donosiš samostalno,

673
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:43,880
 da na neki način

674
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,000
 tražiš duhovnika,

675
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:46,840
 osobu koja zrelaja od tobe,

676
00:31:46,840 --> 00:31:48,380
 pratitelja ili prijatelja

677
00:31:48,380 --> 00:31:49,520
 koji te dobro poznaje,

678
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:51,080
 koji će plakat kad ti plaćeš,

679
00:31:51,080 --> 00:31:52,840
 koji ti neće davati

680
00:31:52,840 --> 00:31:54,360
 paušalne i površne savjete,

681
00:31:54,360 --> 00:31:55,540
 koji te zna u dušu,

682
00:31:55,540 --> 00:31:57,340
 koji zna tamo gdje zabrijavaš,

683
00:31:57,340 --> 00:31:58,960
 koji zna tamo gdje

684
00:31:58,960 --> 00:32:01,040
