694
00:32:15,060 --> 00:32:16,240
 Zato što vas ona čuva

695
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:18,400
 i ona je vaš korektiv.

696
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:22,320
 Zato što se nekad kao obraćenici

697
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:24,700
 ili nekad kao izreli vjernici

698
00:32:24,700 --> 00:32:26,280
 zanesemo nekim nagovorima,

699
00:32:26,280 --> 00:32:27,500
 počnemo donositi odluke

700
00:32:27,500 --> 00:32:28,780
 koje su pomalo i sulude

701
00:32:28,780 --> 00:32:30,480
 i možemo ući u drugu krajnost,

702
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:31,360
 a to da postavimo

703
00:32:31,360 --> 00:32:32,840
 ne siloviti,

704
00:32:32,840 --> 00:32:33,740
 nego silnici,

705
00:32:33,740 --> 00:32:35,160
 bagjeriste,

706
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:37,000
 rušimo sve pred sobom,

707
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:37,580
 gazimo,

708
00:32:37,580 --> 00:32:38,640
 oholi smo,

709
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:40,460
 ne vidimo kad smo zabrijali,

710
00:32:40,460 --> 00:32:41,280
 kad griješimo

711
00:32:41,280 --> 00:32:43,020
 i ne slušamo savjete bližnjih.

712
00:32:43,020 --> 00:32:44,440
 To se isto može dogoditi.

713
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:46,920
 I zato ako imate zajednicu prijatelja

714
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:48,500
 i ako vam dugo već

715
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:49,220
 neko nije dao

716
00:32:49,220 --> 00:32:50,320
 neku bratsku opomenu

717
00:32:50,320 --> 00:32:51,000
 ili kritiku,

718
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:53,000
 zapitajte se

719
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,560
 možda niste na dobro mjestu.

720
00:32:54,560 --> 00:32:57,020
 Možda niste na dobro mjestu

721
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:58,100
 iz razloga

