728
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:14,720
 Ako vam dugo nisu

729
00:33:14,780 --> 00:33:15,720
 da li opomenu kritiku,

730
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:17,400
 to ne znači da ste na dobrom putu.

731
00:33:17,400 --> 00:33:18,480
 Razmislite.

732
00:33:18,480 --> 00:33:20,160
 Možda je problem to što ne možete

733
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:21,160
 poslušati kritiku.

734
00:33:21,160 --> 00:33:22,160
 To je jedna stvar.

735
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,380
 Znači morate imati osobu

736
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:24,940
 pored sebe koja je zrelija u vjeri

737
00:33:24,940 --> 00:33:25,720
 da doneste dobro

738
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:27,000
 s kojom ćete razlučiti,

739
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,180
 staviti plusave i minuse.

740
00:33:28,580 --> 00:33:30,140
 Ali kaže dalje, 13.

741
00:33:30,140 --> 00:33:32,020
 I na savjet srca svoga pazi

742
00:33:32,020 --> 00:33:33,740
 jer nemaš nikog vjernijeg od njega.

743
00:33:33,740 --> 00:33:34,960
 Prevažno.

744
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:36,240
 Imat mir u srcu.

745
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:38,300
 Pričali smo o strahovima.

746
00:33:38,300 --> 00:33:40,280
 Neće bit mirno srce

747
00:33:40,280 --> 00:33:41,240
 ak si pun strahova

748
00:33:41,240 --> 00:33:43,060
 i donosiš odluku i straha i emocije.

749
00:33:43,060 --> 00:33:44,560
 Neće bit mirno.

750
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:46,080
 Zato, kaže,

751
00:33:46,080 --> 00:33:47,500
 bolje predkazuje

