00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:54,380
 utisno sve te želje

756
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:56,240
 i one odgađanjem samo rastu.

757
00:33:56,240 --> 00:34:00,760
 Znači, dvije kvačice.

758
00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:03,140
 Pobožnik, duhovnik, savjetnik.

759
00:34:03,140 --> 00:34:05,100
 Druga kvačica, mir u srcu.

760
00:34:05,100 --> 00:34:06,520
 Potpuni mir u srcu

761
00:34:06,520 --> 00:34:08,020
