00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:37,260
 Ne raduje se tvoje grešci

777
00:34:37,260 --> 00:34:38,120
 i tvoje pogrešci

778
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:40,280
 i želi da doneseš ispravne odluke.

